						<h2>Common Goal: Simplicity</h2>
						<p>
						</p>
						<ol>
							<li class="fragment">Perfection is finally attained not when there is no longer anything to add, but when there is no longer anything to take away
 --- Antoine de Saint-Exupéry</li>
